div.div:
Enter: a bunch of cool guys who look like they got that unapproachable swag. But let's be realthat's not the true them. They're just a bunch of dorks who've got the act down pat. So sit back, grab some popcorn and enjoy watching a bunch of goofy guys try to look cool all day every day.
(Source: Yen Press)
Tomodachi no Imouto ga Ore ni dake Uzai

My best friend is the only one who has my spare keys, but for some reason, his little sister always sneaks into my room... Ooboshi Akiteru is a high school boy who is the very definition of ordinary. He leads an efficient life while being content with his unmemorable existence until his days are completely changed by Kohinata Iroha, the younger sister of his only best friend, Kohinata Ozuma. She pesters Akiteru daily to the point he finds himself caught up in all kinds of troublesome situations. Whats more, he meets other girls who also have attitudes that are hard to deal with! Annoying and cute girls are the best! The popular, teenage romantic comedy begins now! (Source: MANGA UP!)
